
Dear Colleague:

As part of a select group of Energy Professionals, you are invited to
preview our newest free information tool: Energy Central Direct.

Energy Central Direct brings together the best information delivered
by Energy Central and leading industry researchers, analysts and
knowledge providers. This valuable service delivers directly to your
desktop through HTML e-mail.

You can customize your daily e-mail by adding specific content (such
as news, electric prices, events, jobs and more). You can personalize
each selection, showing just the items that are most important to you.
To sign up for your free, personalized Energy Central Direct, please
follow this link: http://www.energycentral.com/sections/ecdirect.

You will be presented with three screens that allow you to step through
the process of creating, customizing and previewing your personal
edition of Energy Central Direct. On the following business day you
will begin receiving your custom Energy Central Direct e-mail.

Register today to receive industry news your way.

